  <p>
  <b><i style="color:red">Email Gateway</i></b>
  <ul>
   <p> If you wish to try out the new email gateway, simply send an email to zentrack@phpzen.net with a subject of help, and that will get you started.  Note that you will need to add your email address to the notify list for a ticket before you can perform actions on it.
  </ul>
  <p>
  <b><i style="color:red">Simple Ticket Create Via Email</i></b>
  <ul>
   <p>To create a ticket using the simple email create utility, send an email to newticket@phpzen.net.  The subject becomes the title, the body becomes the details of the ticket. (the ticket will appear in the Tech Support bin)
  </ul>
  <P>Visit the zenTrack development site <a href='http://sourceforge.net/projects/zentrack/'>http://sourceforge.net/projects/zentrack/</a> for project and support information.
